e. Require the Municipal Accountant to update the columns in WOABSLC pertaining to births of offspring and stock dispositions, and draw necessary journal entries to adjust the balance of Breeding Stocks in the books of accounts. Likewise, provide the necessary adjusting journal entry to record the four calves and three goats purchased in November 2018 including the changes in fair market value; and
f. Require the Supply Officer to prepare the WOABSPC using the information provided by the Municipal Accountant and Municipal Agriculturist.

